  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 190&deg;C/ 170&deg;C (fan)/ 375&deg;F/ Gas 5 <span class=\"text-highlight\">and boil a kettle</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Cut the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways and wash carefully to remove any grit from between the leaves</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Slice the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely, discarding the tough tops, outer leaves and root end<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></span></p>\r\n<p>Slice the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thick discs</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Lato; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>chicken stock cube</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>clotted cream</strong>, <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>&nbsp;with 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [75ml]</span><strong> milk</strong>&nbsp;and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced leeks</strong> and <strong>potatoes</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Pour over the <strong>creamy&nbsp;stock </strong>and cover the dish tightly with <strong>tin foil</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the dish to one side of the lined baking tray&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>baby gammon</strong> dry with<strong> kitchen paper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>baby gammon</strong> to the other side of the baking tray and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 25-35 min or until the <strong>potatoes</strong> are almost cooked</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Use the rest of this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are almost cooked, sprinkle the <strong>grated cheese</strong> over the<strong> leek and potato gratin</strong></p>\r\n<p>Return to the oven, uncovered, for a further 5-10 min until everything is cooked through, golden and piping hot</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is cooked through, remove the tray from the oven and allow to stand for 5 min</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>shredded spring greens</strong>&nbsp;to a colander over the sink and pour over the&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong>&nbsp;until the greens are bright green and wilted&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1577.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
